Package utilities

Class Foods

java.lang.Object
utilities.Foods
public class Foods extends Object
The Foods class contains all foods mentioned in product domain glossary, alongside their calories and densities. Able to add more ingredients and load in existing added ingredients.
Version:
10/25/24
Author:
f24team3d
